{"tid":1953442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國醫生超速駕駛 明尼蘇達州警員無抄牌更送5個口罩","createTime":"2020-04-01T07:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T13:06:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1057,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":111,"replies":[{"pid":"96c043a421a36bda9c81069f6f12c750d776ff05","tid":1953442,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T07:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1585664817_MB-1280w.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1585664817_MB-1280w.JPG&h=a1f1f958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1585664819_Xp-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1585664819_Xp-1280w.jpg&h=bbd7251f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/3/1585664821_ma-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F3%2F1585664821_ma-1280w.jpg&h=b3dc75a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國明尼蘇達州女醫生薩羅希(Sarosh Ashraf Janjua)，本月21日因超速駕駛而被警員攔截，她在Facebook上憶述，當時警員說：「超速是不負責任的行為，若你受傷，不但佔用醫療資源，更會少了一個醫生協助病人。」正當薩羅希以為要收告票時，交到她手的竟是5個N95口罩&mdash;&mdash;原來該警員見到她手袋內有兩個用過的N95口罩，擔心她重用，故把州政府給予自己的口罩送給她。薩羅希分享此故事後，獲明尼蘇達州警方回應，感謝她為民眾努力抗疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E7%BE%8E%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%B6%85%E9%80%9F%E9%A7%95%E9%A7%9B-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%84%A1%E6%8A%84%E7%89%8C%E6%9B%B4%E9%80%815%E5%80%8B%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-213596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25A7%2595%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25